OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F335A1784567932
OL,3,CTributes to 'unforgettable' teen who
OL,4,Cdied in lake incident
OL,6,FThe family of a boy who was the second
OL,7,Fteenager to die in the same stretch of
OL,8,Fwater in a matter of weeks say he was
OL,9,F"vibrant, energetic and unforgettable".
OL,11,FSixteen-year-old Iretomiwa Abiodun
OL,12,FMicheal, known as "Tomiwa", died after
OL,13,Fgetting into difficulty at Swanholme
OL,14,FLakes in Lincoln on 9 July 2026.
OL,16,FHe was treated at the scene by
OL,17,Fparamedics and Lincolnshire Police
OL,18,Fsaid he initially responded to
OL,19,Ftreatment, but he died later in
OL,20,Fhospital with his family by his side.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
