PN,33502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F335A1784567932
OL,3,CTributes to 'unforgettable' teen who
OL,4,Cdied in lake incident
OL,6,FIn a statement his family said:
OL,7,F"Tomiwa was a vibrant, energetic, and
OL,8,Funforgettable young man whose presence
OL,9,Filluminated every space he entered.
OL,10,FHis laughter, warmth, and joyful
OL,11,Fspirit touched countless lives.
OL,13,F"As the eldest of four brothers,
OL,14,FTomiwa embraced his role with pride
OL,15,Fand maturity.
OL,17,F"He was a natural leader, a protector,
OL,18,Fa guide, and a constant source of
OL,19,Fencouragement.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,336,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F335A1784567932
OL,3,CTributes to 'unforgettable' teen who
OL,4,Cdied in lake incident
OL,6,F"His younger brothers adored him, and
OL,7,Fhe cared for them with tenderness,
OL,8,Falways making them smile and
OL,9,Fsupporting them in every way.
OL,11,F"He was our firstborn, our pride, and
OL,12,Fhe honoured his parents by following
OL,13,Finstructions respectfully and living
OL,14,Fwith discipline, purpose and integrity.
OL,16,F"Tomiwa leaves behind a legacy of
OL,17,Flove, faith, discipline, joy, and
OL,18,Fcompassion."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
