PN,33504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F335A1784567932
OL,3,CTributes to 'unforgettable' teen who
OL,4,Cdied in lake incident
OL,6,FTomiwa's death came after 15-year-old
OL,7,FDeclan Sawyer drowned at Swanholme
OL,8,FLakes on 24 May.
OL,10,FThat incident prompted calls for more
OL,11,Frangers in parks in the city, who
OL,12,Fbegan their patrols of the area on
OL,13,FFriday 17 July.
OL,15,FCouncil leader Naomi Tweddle told the
OL,16,FLocal Democracy Reporting Service that
OL,17,Fthe lakes, which are former gravel
OL,18,Fpits, were "never designed for
OL,19,Fswimming", with unseen dangers below
OL,20,Fthe surface.
OL,26,@zD@LOU{D@IO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
