PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F335A1784567932
OL,3,CTributes to 'unforgettable' teen who
OL,4,Cdied in lake incident
OL,6,FShe added: "Swimming in lakes is
OL,7,Fexceptionally dangerous. If people see
OL,8,Fanything, it needs to be reported."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/5
